editnotify-desc: Tirisibu zaŋ n-ti yaɣili yoobu bee maliniŋ lahabali nyɛbu
editnotify-flyout-message: Lahabali nyɛbu zaŋ n-ti yaɣili maliniŋ
editnotify-flyout-message-page-create: Lahabali baŋbu zaŋ n-ti yaɣili nambu
editnotify-email-subject-message-templat: Yaɣili "$2": darisa zaŋ n-ti "$3" taɣibu n-ti "$4"
editnotify-email-body-message:
Maliniŋ daa niŋ yaɣili "$1" puuni. A nyari la lahabali ŋɔ dama a lihiri la tuma ŋɔ
"$2".
editnotify-email-body-message-page-creat: Yaɣili "$1" daa nam ya. A nyari la lahabali ŋɔ dama a a nyɛla ŋun lihiri tuma ŋɔ nambu yaɣa.
editnotify-email-body-message-template: Darisa zaŋ n-ti "$1" daa taɣiya bin din gbaai "$2" hali ni "$3" tɛmplet "$4" yaɣili "$5" puuni. A nyari la lahabali ŋɔ dama a nyɛla ŋun lihiri tuma ŋɔ  "$6".
